          <li>
            <svg width="18" height="18" fill="none" stroke="#16a34a" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            Valuacion de mercado con rango de precio
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg width="18" height="18" fill="none" stroke="#16a34a" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            Market timing: es buen momento para vender?
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg width="18" height="18" fill="none" stroke="#16a34a" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            Demand score del barrio (0-100)
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg width="18" height="18" fill="none" stroke="#16a34a" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            Sell vs rent — que conviene mas
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg width="18" height="18" fill="none" stroke="#16a34a" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            Renovation ROI — cuanto ganarias renovando
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg width="18" height="18" fill="none" stroke="#16a34a" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            Comparacion con 3 barrios similares
          </li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/evaluar" class="btn btn-primary btn-block" style="margin-top:auto">Evaluar gratis</a>
      </div>
      <div class="value-column">
        <div class="value-header premium">Premium — inteligencia completa</div>
        <ul class="value-list">
          <li>
            <svg width="18" height="18" fill="none" stroke="#d97706" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            Todo lo gratuito, mas:
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg width="18" height="18" fill="none" stroke="#d97706" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            Forecasting avanzado con modelos predictivos
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg width="18" height="18" fill="none" stroke="#d97706" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            Propuesta del mejor deal (ej: "alquila ahora, vende en 3 anos")
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg width="18" height="18" fill="none" stroke="#d97706" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            Monitoreo de mercado y alertas de precios
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg width="18" height="18" fill="none" stroke="#d97706" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            Inmobiliarias sugeridas + staging virtual con IA
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg width="18" height="18" fill="none" stroke="#d97706" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            PDF profesional + simulacion de ingresos completa
          </li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/precios" class="btn btn-outline btn-block" style="margin-top:auto">Ver precios</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- What we analyze -->
<section class="section section-alt">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-center">
      <h2 class="section-title">Que analiza nuestra inteligencia artificial</h2>
      <p class="section-desc">No es solo ubicacion y metros cuadrados.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="features-grid">
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg width="24" height="24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Datos de mercado en tiempo real</h3>
        <p>Precio por m2, tendencia anual, inventario, demanda. Datos de +32,000 propiedades actualizados trimestralmente.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg width="24" height="24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 6v6l4 2"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Predicciones a 5 anos</h3>
        <p>Proyecciones de precio basadas en tendencias historicas. Sabe si conviene vender hoy o esperar.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg width="24" height="24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z"/><path d="M2 17l10 5 10-5"/><path d="M2 12l10 5 10-5"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Estrategia personalizada</h3>
        <p>Vender vs alquilar vs temporario. Renovar vs vender asi. Cada decision respaldada con numeros.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg width="24" height="24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><circle cx="8.5" cy="8.5" r="1.5"/><path d="M21 15l-5-5L5 21"/></svg>
